
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xia-netext-flow-binding-02.txt'>
    <title>"Flow Binding in Proxy Mobile IPv6", Frank Xia, Behcet Sarikaya</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xia-netext-flow-binding-02.txt</link>
    <description>This document introduces extensions to Proxy Mobile IPv6 that allows networks dynamically binding IP flows to different interfaces of a mobile node.  Mobile Access Gateways can move flows to other mobile access gateways by establishing flow bindings at the local mobility anchor.  Local mobility anchor sends packets from the offloaded flow seamlessly to the new mobile access gateway.</description>
    <dc:date>2010-06-24T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
